  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/operationPlanPreCondition">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty"/>
    <rdfs:label>operationPlanPreCondition</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">The ActionPreCondition to check/that would be checked whenever the OperationPlan will be executed/is executed.

Alignment:
- *PEP*: OperationPlan (Procedures) may be linked to some description of the input, hence `operationPlanPreCondition` is a kind of `pep:hasInput`.
- *BBO*: From the BPMN perspective, the `operationPlanPreCondition` is the description of what may activate the realization of a given Task, hence it is a kind of `BBO:has_activationCondition`.
</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/OperationPlan"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/ActionPreCondition"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/pep/hasInput"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="https://www.irit.fr/recherches/MELODI/ontologies/BBO#has_activationCondition"/>
    <vs:term_status>stable</vs:term_status>
    <skos:changeNote>Change in v0.2:
- Adding pep:hasInput.
- Adding rdfs:subPropertyOf BBO::has_activationCondition.
</skos:changeNote>
    <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/"/>
  </rdf:Description>
